name: fog
description:
A man on the way to open his umbrella on a foggy morning. 
Taken in front of Christ Church College in Oxford, UK.

The picture is taken with a Nikon D80 with 18-135mm lens.
It is digitally enhanced for a desired effect.

Printed on HahnemÜhle Photo Rag Baryta 315 gsm.
(Mould-made, 100% Cotton, Acid free, Smooth "Baryta" Gloss). 
Unframed. 
Size: A4 with a border of 4cm all around outside the A4.

After you order the picture, it will take between 10-15 days before receiving the print.
The shipping is included in the price.

If you want a different picture from my website (www.simonabarbu.com) or from my flickr gallery 
( http://www.flickr.com/photos/createsimona/ ), please contact me.

Thanks for stopping by.
